text: Delicious comforting Malay food. Friendly owners. Mee Siam is their hot favourite
Delicious nasi padang at such an affordable price! They also have mee rebus, mee soto & nasi lemak.
Be careful when selecting the food items. Always choose the dishes and dont let the person choose for you. You will tend to get the worst meat/portion for them to clear their dishes.
Delicious Malay food at low price. Selling Nasi Campur, Nasi Lemak, Mee Siam, Mee Rebus, & my favorite Fried Tofu. Friendly owners.  Stall closes on Fridays.
